📘 PR. 1 Fundamental Booster – README
📌 Project Description

This project is created to practice basic to intermediate spreadsheet formulas in Google Sheets / Excel.
The project covers formulas like IF, COUNTIFS, SUMIFS, VLOOKUP, INDEX-MATCH, TEXT, INDIRECT, OFFSET, FILTER, Date-Time, and Math functions.

The goal of this project is to understand how formulas work and how they are used in real data analysis.

